To make PyCharm complete function for customer package
(1) make a package with __init__.py (empty is OK)
(2) Edit PyCharm setting
'PyCharm -> Preferences -> Project Interpreter' or 'File -> Setting -> Project Interpreter'
Press 'setting' (gear icon on the right top) -> '+' to add 'more' -> add 'Interpreter path'
to add customer package path

It is convenient to make pyenv or virtualenv to save and manage the packages for
different usages.